# Google Gemini API key for the in-app AI planner (hero "Plan my day").
# Get a free key at https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
# Copy this file to ".env" and fill in your key, then restart `npm run dev`.
#
# NOTE: This is a frontend-only app, so the key is bundled into the client and
# is visible to anyone using the app. Use a personal/free key and restrict it
# (e.g. by referrer/quota) in Google AI Studio. For a public deployment, put a
# proxy in front instead of shipping the key.
VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY=

# Optional: override the model (defaults to gemini-2.5-flash).
# The app auto-falls back to other flash models on quota (429) / overload (503).
VITE_GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-2.5-flash
